                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7949" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1239</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">1560 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大厦将倾，雪松系族何以维系？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">How the Cedar Holdings Survives from Trust Crisis?</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">金鑫，王赟，孙钰枫</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">浙江工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雪松控股集团有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">贸易与金融业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">18 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">雪松系；金字塔结构；利益侵占；流动性陷阱</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Cedar Holdings, Pyramid Structure, Controlling Shareholder Expropriation, Liquidity Trap</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经过多年商业版图的探索和拓展，雪松控股一度发展成为中国大宗商品领军企业。伴随着积极的多元化扩张，雪松控股成为一家覆盖大宗商品供应链、化工新材料、文化旅游康养、社区智联服务和社会公益服务五大产业板块的民营企业，最终实现了连续四年上榜“世界五百强”。然而，随着多名雪松控股的重要成员失联，实际控制人被采取刑事强制措施，多家主体被立案调查，“雪松系”的串联风险逐步暴露。本案例以系族企业“雪松系”金字塔结构为切入点，描述“雪松系”实际控制人张劲如何构建商业帝国，又缘何身陷囹圄，引发学生思考民营系族企业如何实现有效的内部治理与可持续发展。本案例旨在引导学生理解系族企业中大股东利益侵占途径和后果，以及如何防范。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">After years of exploration and expansion of the commercial landscape, Cedar Holdings has developed into a leading Chinese commodity company. Accompanied by active diversified expansion, Cedar Holdings has become a private enterprise covering five major industrial sectors: commodity supply chain, chemical new materials, cultural tourism and health care, community smart networking services, and social welfare services, ultimately achieving four consecutive years of being listed as one of the &quot;Fortune 500&quot;. However, as several important executives of Cedar Holdings lost contact, the actual controller was taken criminal coercive measures, and some entities have been filed for investigation, a lot of members of Cedar Groups have also suffered from risk contagion. Taking the &quot;Cedar Groups&quot; pyramid structure as the starting point, this case describes how Zhang Jin, the actual controller constructed a commercial empire and why he was taken criminal coercive measures, which guides students to think about how private family enterprises can achieve effective internal governance and sustainable development. This case aims to help students to understand the ways and consequences of benefit expropriation of controlling shareholders in business groups, as well as how to prevent benefit expropriation.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务报表分析》、《高级财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GONE理论；委托代理理论；信息不对称理论；利益相关者理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
